1) create a dir --> mkdir chainlit_rag
2) Create .env File with the Following Content Inside the Folder -->
[cohere]
api_key = Your COHERE API KEY1

You can obtain the API key by registering yourself at: https://dashboard.cohere.com/api-keys

example --> new text document(sample given)
3) Download the model file from the link and save it to the current working directory, i.e., inside the chainlit_rag folder.
https://huggingface.co/TheBloke/zephyr-7B-beta-GGUF/blob/main/zephyr-7b-beta.Q4_K_M.gguf


